                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>If a Small or larger creature dies within a Pod Prison, the pod transforms into an adult moonflower with full Hit Points after [[/gmr 1d4 #hours]]{1d4 hours} of growth. The newly formed moonflower has its own consciousness, but some aspect of its trunk or blossoms typically resemble the creature that died within. The dead creature's equipment remains inside the new moonflower and can be retrieved if the moonflower is slain.</p>"
                },
